This committee recommends that the government amend the Criminal Code to allow assisted suicide and euthanasia, where appropriate, from a patient deemed competent to make such a decision.
At the start of the game, experts cite a recent survey by the Economist Intelligence Unit, which compared the quality of death in 40 countries of the planet.
